components.name: Load Customer Segment CSV
components.description: Loads customer segmentation data from a CSV file into an inmemory dataset for downstream marketing channels.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies; this is the first task in the pipeline.

components.name: Send Email Campaign
components.description: Sends an email marketing campaign to premium customers using the loaded segment data.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful loading of customer segment data.

components.name: Send SMS Campaign
components.description: Sends an SMS marketing campaign with exclusive deals to customers using the loaded segment data.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful loading of customer segment data.

components.name: Send Push Notification
components.description: Sends a push notification campaign to mobile app users using the loaded segment data.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful loading of customer segment data.

connections.purpose: Send push notifications to mobile app users

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

sources: Customer segment CSV file stored on the local filesystem
sinks: Email campaign execution results sent to the Email Delivery Service API
SMS campaign execution results sent to the SMS Gateway API
Push notification campaign execution results sent to the Push Notification Service API
intermediate_datasets: customer_segment_dataset (inmemory representation of the loaded CSV)
